Squats - Am i doing them correctly?

   I'm trying to increase the muscle mass of my legs and so have turned to
   squats. I'm currently using the smith machine with about 180lbs. After
   the exercise (3x10 squats) and getting some rest i find the only part
   of my body that is sore is my butt. I was hoping for pain in the legs
   but this never occurs.... [114]show more I'm trying to increase the
   muscle mass of my legs and so have turned to squats. I'm currently
   using the smith machine with about 180lbs. After the exercise (3x10
   squats) and getting some rest i find the only part of my body that is
   sore is my butt. I was hoping for pain in the legs but this never
   occurs. I'm all for a tighter behind but my goal is larger legs.
   Am i performing squats correctly using the smith machine? or should i
   be using this apparatus at all?
   Update: ** When i say leg muscles i mean my thighs.
   Follow
